    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.5</title>
      <description><![CDATA[Bug fixes and polish.

• Voice isolation / mic indicator now clears immediately when a recording session ends — previously the engine stayed warm for the entire app lifetime.
• Fresh AVAudioEngine per session; simpler lifecycle, no lingering hardware allocation.
• Fixed cancel-while-starting race that could leave an orphan engine running if the hotkey was released during engine setup.
• Start sound no longer gets cut off by voice-processing setup — it now plays after the engine is ready.
• ASR model download progress bar is smooth instead of only showing 1% → 49% → 50% → done.
• LLM result card height reduced ~20% — more compact without being cramped.
• Removed the "Apple Silicon" tag from the speech model list (it was redundant).]]></description>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 00:36:02 +0200</pubDate>
